<mvc:View controllerName="ui5.ecosystem.demo.simpleapp.controller.Main" displayBlock="true" xmlns="sap.m" xmlns:core="sap.ui.core" xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" xmlns:mod="ui5-module">
  <Page id="page" title="{i18n>appTitle}">
    <headerContent>
      <core:Icon color="#1873B4" src="sap-icon://sap-ui5" size="2rem" />
    </headerContent>
    <content>
      <VBox alignItems="Center" justifyContent="Center" height="100%">
        <Button text="Don't press me!" press="onBoo" />
        <mod:Chart title="Some Chart" color="blue">
          <mod:ChartRecord label="Value 1" value="100" />
          <mod:ChartRecord label="Value 2" value="50" />
          <mod:ChartRecord label="Value 3" value="200" />
          <mod:ChartRecord label="Value 4" value="150" />
          <mod:ChartRecord label="Value 5" value="125" />
        </mod:Chart>
      </VBox>
    </content>
  </Page>
</mvc:View>
